    "code": "import whest as we\n\na = we.arange(10)\n\na\n\nwe.clip(a, 1, 8)\n\nwe.clip(a, 8, 1)\n\nwe.clip(a, 3, 6, out=a)\n\na\n\na = we.arange(10)\n\na\n\nwe.clip(a, [3, 4, 1, 1, 1, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4], 8)",
